root: ^Let's see... Hm, no, I've gotten everything done already, I guess.
^(Right on cue, O'Ryan enters the Diner.)
^Everything's all done and set for the day!
^(O'Ryan takes out my envelope and places it in my hand)
^(Just like that, O'Ryan turns and leaves through the portal.)
^Alright... Looks like I'm on their good side!
^Well, since I finished early... Guess I can head out!
